featured_reviews.review_id:
Through the Indian news papers (PTI) in the year 1984 got to know there was a very old dead body (may be 100 years old as per the locals) was recovered while Tamil labourers digging for the renovation of the Mosque.

Body and its cloth (kaffan) covering was not damaged or eaten by the grave.  Beautiful nice smell was emitting from the grave. Body's beard & hair was shining like silver. This was the Report of all news papers.
So I had been to this place after reading that news.
I wondered about that dead person status with Almighty. What are all the good things done by him to gain this state. They are the Friends of Allaah as told by Allaah in Qur'aan.

As per the Prophet's tradition Prophet's body won't get decay and damaged until the resurrection. And also the pious persons dead body. It is being proved occasionally.

Oh! God give us all better than that position and forgive our sins which we are doing knowingly and unknowingly.
